		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Debugbook option &quot;Act3 → LOW - Auntie Ethel's Revenge → Hag was defeated in Act I&#xD;&#xA;- Equip one of the hag masks found here, -2355; 4; -126&#xD;&#xA;- Talk to masked Quenora, -122; 26; -95" />
